Robert Metz was named managing director and Margaret Jackson was named vice president of the U.S. unit of this London-based merchant banking firm, C.J. Lawrence, Morgan Grenfell Inc.
They will jointly be responsible for establishing a private-placement operation in the corporate finance department of the New York-based unit.
Each had been in the private-placement department of Bear, Stearns & Co. with the same titles. 

